          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Living Independently for Extended Time Act or the LIFETIME Act </b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to award grants to enable eligible states to develop innovative programs to meet the unique need for long-term services and supports in the state. </p>]]></text>
